2.1.3 - 2022-12-22
    Added one random radio station into "For You"
    Better search results when cold started from assistant
    Sleep timer to pause instead of stop
    Bugfixes specific to Android 12 & up

2.1.2 - 2022-12-11
    Better handling of session expired while refreshing cached lists
    Minor UI improvements
    Bugfixes

2.1.1 - 2022-12-03
    Radio Stations fade in
    Bugfixes

2.1 - 2022-11-27
    Minimum Android version is now 10
    Dropped support for Ampache version 4, minimum is 5.0.0
    Support radio stations
    Separate equalizer settings for radio stations
    Less recommendations in "For You"
    Refresh UI after options changed
    Sleep timer
    Minor UI improvements
    Bugfixes

2.0.15 - 2022-11-07
    Show queue in Android Auto, when playing a playlist, an album, or similar items

2.0.14 - 2022-05-03
    Support playlist art (requires refresh of playlists)
    Workarounds for favorites issues in server

2.0.13 - 2022-04-10
    Search now includes tags (genres)
    Better landscape layout

